comments: Mobley (CLE) is already in Grant's (DET) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Bey (DET) and LeVert (CLE) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Stewart (DET) is already in LeVert's (CLE) path and does not deliver contact.
Markkanen (CLE) is moving alongside Bey's (DET) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
LeVert (CLE) is already in Stewart's (DET) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Stewart (DET) is moving alongside Mobley's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Grant (DET) loses control of the ball on his own prior to any marginal arm contact form Mobley (CLE).  Mobley then cleanly steals the ball from Grant.
Garland (CLE) and Joseph (DET) briefly engage and disengage off ball in the backcourt.
Cunningham (DET) places his hand on Okoro's (CLE) opposite hip and initiates contact that allows Cunningham to deflect the ball away from Okoro.
Joseph (DET) and Okoro (CLE) come together at the same spot and incidental contact occurs as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Joseph (DET) legally contests Markkanen's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Stewart (DET) is already in Okoro's (CLE) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Markkanen (CLE) is moving alongside Cunningham's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Okoro (CLE) and Stewart (DET) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Grant (DET) brushes Garland's (CLE) arm and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Bey (DET) applies a stayed hand to Garland's (CLE) arm and marginal contact occurs as Garland completes his intended pass.
Bey (DET) cleanly dislodges the ball from Garland (CLE).
